---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";

import ContactCTA from "../components/ContactCTA.astro";
import Hero from "../components/Hero.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
	title="About | S. M. Anaëlle B."
	description="About S. M. Anaëlle B."
>
	<div class="stack gap-20">
		<main class="wrapper about">
			<Hero
				title="About"
				tagline="Thanks for stopping by. Read below to learn more about myself and my background."
			/>

			<section>
				<h2 class="section-title">Background</h2>
				<div class="content">
					<p>
						Python backend developer with passion for designing and
						implementing solutions robust. With solid experience in the
						development of software and database management, I am specialized in
						the creation of scalable and efficient applications. SKILLS keys:
						Programming languages: In-depth mastery of Python, with particular
						expertise in frameworks such as Django and Flask. Database
						management: Experience in design, implementation and optimization of
						databases relational, notably MySQL and PostgreSQL. Architecture
						software: Design and development of software architectures
						efficient, promoting modularity, reusability and ease of
						maintenance. APIs and Web Services: Creation of APIs RESTful and
						other web services to enable communication fluid between the
						different parts of an application. Deployment and management: Use of
						deployment tools like Docker and orchestration with Kubernetes.
						Server management with technologies such as Nginx and Apache.
						Automated tests: Implementation place of unit and functional tests
						to ensure the quality of the code and facilitate updates. Security:
						Integration of security practices in development, including
						validation data, protection against SQL injections and management
						authorizations. Professional experience: [Name of the company] -
						[Period] Python Backend Developer Design and development of an
						inventory management application used by the logistics team.
						Implementation of RESTful APIs to enable integration with other
						systems. SQL Query Optimization to improve database performance.
					</p>
					
				</div>
			</section>
			<section>
				<h2 class="section-title">Education</h2>
				<div class="content">
					<p>Corporis voluptates tenetur laudantium.</p>
				</div>
			</section>
			<section>
				<h2 class="section-title">Skills</h2>
				<div class="content">
					<p>officia unde omnis</p>
				</div>
			</section>
		</main>

		<ContactCTA />
	</div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
	.about {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 3.5rem;
	}

	img {
		margin-top: 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 1.5rem;
		box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
	}

	section {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 0.5rem;
		color: var(--gray-200);
	}

	.section-title {
		grid-column-start: 1;
		font-size: var(--text-xl);
		color: var(--gray-0);
	}

	.content {
		grid-column: 2 / 4;
	}

	.content :global(a) {
		text-decoration: 1px solid underline transparent;
		text-underline-offset: 0.25em;
		transition: text-decoration-color var(--theme-transition);
	}

	.content :global(a:hover),
	.content :global(a:focus) {
		text-decoration-color: currentColor;
	}

	@media (min-width: 50em) {
		.about {
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: 1fr 60% 1fr;
		}

		.about > :global(:first-child) {
			grid-column-start: 2;
		}

		section {
			display: contents;
			font-size: var(--text-lg);
		}
	}
</style>
